                    <li>The average size of library is 600bp for 16s pool.</li>
                    <li>The libraries were sequenced on Illumina Miseq platform (2 x 300 bp chemistry) to generate ~1,00,000 reads/sample.</li>
                <% } %>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 7 -->
        <div id="section-7" class="section">
            <h2>7. Data Generation</h2>
            <p>The data statistics of the reads obtained for each sample is provided in the below Table.</p>
            <div class="table-wrapper">
                <div class="table-title">Table 1: Raw reads data statistics</div>
                <table>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Sample ID</th>
                            <th>PE seq</th>
